title: Determining the shape of each graph.
text: First, you need to determine the shape of each box plot. All through tend to have more greater values which means they are all skewed right.

title: Understanding what skewness implies.
text: Secondly, you must understand what a right skew means in context. Here, it shows that the ages of the top 50% of buyers are more variable than the ages of the lower 50%.
